name: Ship it out!
description:
Factory needs your help getting boxes out of the warehouse! Fix the conveyour and deliver boxes to the customers!

Game music by: David Fesliyan

You can check his work at:

https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/

CONTROLS:    MOUSE Left Click to walk around.

This is a short version of the game. Please leave feedback in the comments! Thank you!
